name: transactionIndex
description: the zero-indexed position of the transaction in the block

name: fromName
description: the name for this from address

name: toName
description: the name for this to address

name: gasOut.
description: the amount of gas cost for the transaction

name: status
description: `1` on transaction suceess, `null` if tx precedes Byzantium, `0` otherwise

name: isError
description: whether the transaction resulted in an error

name: contractAddress
description: the address of the newly created contract, if any

name: contractAddressName
description: the name for this contract address

name: logs
description: a possibly empty array of logs
